text: Look for delicious iÖGO Cherry Swirl in the grocery Ice Cream and Frozen Dessert aisle. Each spoonful offers tangy vanilla-flavoured frozen yogurt with cherry swirls throughout. Proudly prepared in Canada using 100% Canadian milk and real fruit. Real fruit, real dairy, real fun...in every scoop!
